OL,3,COcean experts call for end to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cdestruction of oceans by fishing'
OL,6,FA group of leading ocean experts call
OL,7,Ffor an end to the "ongoing destruction
OL,8,Fof our oceans by fishing" and say the
OL,9,Fcurrent definition of sustainable
OL,10,Ffishing is "dangerously flawed".
OL,12,FIn a paper published in the journal
OL,13,FOcean Sustainability, the researchers
OL,14,Fcall for stricter rules on fishing, as
OL,15,Fthey say many products marketed as
OL,16,Fsustainable are not.
