OL,3,COcean experts call for end to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cdestruction of oceans by fishing'
OL,6,FThe study says companies and
OL,7,Flegislation needs to do more to
OL,8,Fprotect ecosystems and fisheries - and
OL,9,Fshould take climate change into
OL,10,Fconsideration.
OL,12,FFishing is the leading cause of ocean
OL,13,Fdestruction, with fish populations
OL,14,Ffallen by a third in the last 50 years.
OL,16,FResearchers have laid out 11 "golden
OL,17,Frules" which they say would help renew
OL,18,Ffish populations in order to feed
OL,19,Ffuture generations.
