OL,3,COcean experts call for end to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cdestruction of oceans by fishing'
OL,6,FThese include limiting the size of
OL,7,Fboats and equipment, incorporating
OL,8,Fecosystem protection into fisheries
OL,9,Fmanagement and ending "harmful
OL,10,Fsubsidies" to fisheries.
OL,12,FProfessor Paul Kemp, from the
OL,13,FUniversity of Southampton and a co-
OL,14,Fauthor of the paper, said: "This
OL,15,Finitiative brought together a diverse
OL,16,Fgroup of experts, including those from
OL,17,Ffisheries science, social sciences,
OL,18,Feconomics and conservation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
