OL,3,COcean experts call for end to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cdestruction of oceans by fishing'
OL,6,F"By doing so we were able to develop a
OL,7,Froadmap to move away from the
OL,8,Ftraditional view of fisheries that
OL,9,Ftends to focus on the social and
OL,10,Feconomic context of those who utilise
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"Sustainability, however, requires the
OL,14,Fintegration of the social, economic
OL,15,Fand environmental domains. This paper
OL,16,Fprovides a manifesto that will help
OL,17,Fsecure our fisheries for sustainable
OL,18,Fexploitation by future generations."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
