OL,3,COcean experts call for end to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cdestruction of oceans by fishing'
OL,6,FOther proposed rules including fishing
OL,7,Fless for lower impact, sourcing only
OL,8,Ffrom fisheries with good governance
OL,9,Fand sustainable stocks and placing the
OL,10,Fmost vulnerable species and areas off
OL,11,Flimits.
OL,13,FThey also call for the creation of
OL,14,Ffisheries management systems that
OL,15,Ffairly and transparently distribute
OL,16,Faccess and benefits, apply good
OL,17,Fpractices wherever fishing companies
OL,18,Foperate and apply zero-tolerance to
OL,19,Fcompanies that engage in illegal
OL,20,Ffishing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
