OL,3,COcean experts call for end to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cdestruction of oceans by fishing'
OL,6,FThe researchers say that current
OL,7,Fstandards of sustainability support
OL,8,F"high-capital industrial practices
OL,9,Fwhich benefit the Global North" but
OL,10,Fwhich harm ecosystems and jeopardise
OL,11,F"artisanal fishing, food security, and
OL,12,Fjobs".
OL,14,FLead author Professor Callum Roberts,
OL,15,Fof the University of Exeter, said:
OL,16,F"The current concept of 'sustainable
OL,17,Ffishing', adopted by governments and
OL,18,Fprivate actors since the post-war
OL,19,Fperiod, is scientifically obsolete.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
