OL,3,COcean experts call for end to 'ongoing
OL,4,Cdestruction of oceans by fishing'
OL,6,F"It relies on a simplistic,
OL,7,Fproductivist theory which assumes that
OL,8,Fas long as global catch volumes remain
OL,9,Fbelow a set limit, anyone can fish
OL,10,Fjust about anything, anywhere, with
OL,11,Fany method."
OL,13,FThe paper calls on policymakers,
OL,14,Fretailers, and fishery managers to
OL,15,Facknowledge the failings of current
OL,16,Ffishing practices and prioritise the
OL,17,Fadoption of the proposed golden rules
OL,18,Fwith supermarkets having a "pivotal
OL,19,Frole" in any change.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
